        "Data": [
          "<h1>Applies to</h1>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 6.2</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <h1>What to Do</h1>\r\n  <p>Install critical security patches within a month of them being released.</p>\r\n  <h1>Why</h1>\r\n  <p>Installing critical security patches in a timely manner fixes known vulnerabilities before an attacker can exploit them.</p>\r\n  <h1>How</h1>\r\n  <p>Add a point to the information security policy that requires critical security patches to be installed within a month of being released by the vendor.\r\n</p>"
